major-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast;
mso-bidi-font-family:Arial">一<span lang="EN-US">) </span>个人数字证书是经中国结算<span lang="EN-US">CA</span>系统签发的包含个人信息的数字证书，它用于标志自然人在进行信息交换、电子签名、电子商务等网络活动中的身份。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:13.5pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:
major-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;
